research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Benbrook operates under a council/manager form of government, with seven elected members: the Mayor and six City Council members, all elected at large. There was a discrepancy between sources regarding the Mayor Pro-Tem and the Council Member for Place 5. The Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory was prioritized for the full list of elected officials due to its comprehensive nature for all listed positions, and cross-referenced with the official Benbrook website where possible.
